{"type":"message","id":"cfb20d19","parentId":"1ecf3934","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:46:50.835Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"chat:oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b51b2a47edc90c2c74cb0fd7927e\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"conversation_label\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-04-22 14:46 GMT+8\",\n  \"group_subject\": \"oc_06bd0381650c08be8b7819c0e05e9e92\",\n  \"is_group_chat\": true,\n  \"was_mentioned\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b51b2a47edc90c2c74cb0fd7927e]\nou_268230d4dfea5f51af33421d332e3bd3: @_all 学习理解这个技能：/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-finder-cn，保存到记忆中。"}],"timestamp":1776840410834}}
{"type":"message","id":"336a984b","parentId":"cfb20d19","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:46:53.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求学习 skill-finder-cn 技能，我需要先读取 SKILL.md 文件来了解它的功能和用法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我来学习这个技能 🦐\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bd3d83d54beb470e9a16a657","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-finder-cn/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":33151,"output":102,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33253,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776840410836,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3ef1d7ee-0a44-9d64-9b07-04382b3b13cf"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d80d558a","parentId":"336a984b","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:46:53.889Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_bd3d83d54beb470e9a16a657","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: skill-finder-cn\ndescription: \"Skill 查找器 | Skill Finder. 帮助发现和安装 ClawHub Skills | Discover and install ClawHub Skills. 回答'有什么技能可以X'、'找一个技能' | Answers 'what skill can X', 'find a skill'. 触发词：找 skill、find skill、搜索 skill.\"\nauthor: 赚钱小能手\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: 🔍\n    requires:\n      bins: [clawhub]\n---\n\n# Skill 查找器 v1.0.1\n\n帮助用户发现和安装 ClawHub 上的 Skills。\n\n## 功能\n\n当用户问：\n- \"有什么 skill 可以帮我...？\"\n- \"找一个能做 X 的 skill\"\n- \"有没有 skill 可以...\"\n- \"我需要一个能...的 skill\"\n\n这个 Skill 会帮助搜索 ClawHub 并推荐相关的 Skills。\n\n## 使用方法\n\n### 1. 搜索 Skills\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"<用户需求>\"\n```\n\n### 2. 查看详情（含统计数据）\n\n```bash\nclawhub inspect <skill-name>\n```\n\n或者直接 API 查询 stats：\n\n```bash\ncurl \"https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/skills/<skill-name>\" | jq '.skill.stats'\n```\n\n### 3. 安装 Skill\n\n```bash\nclawhub install <skill-name>\n```\n\n### 4. 验证安装（新增！）\n\n安装后必须验证：\n\n```bash\n# 检查是否安装成功\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n\n# 如果文件存在，说明安装成功\n# 如果文件不存在，说明安装失败\n```\n\n### 5. 检查已安装的 Skill\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\n或者：\n\n```bash\nls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n1. 理解用户需求\n2. 提取关键词\n3. 搜索 ClawHub\n4. 列出相关 Skills（含下载量/stars）\n5. 推荐最合适的 Skill\n6. 安装后验证是否成功\n```\n\n## 输出格式（优化版）\n\n搜索结果应该包含：\n- Skill 名称\n- 简短描述（中文）\n- 下载量\n- Stars 数\n- 是否已安装\n\n```\n🔍 \"时间管理\" 搜索结果：\n\n1. time-management-2\n   描述：有效管理时间，避免过度工作\n   下载：1,234 | Stars: 15 | ✅ 已安装\n\n2. productivity\n   描述：生产力系统，包含目标/任务/习惯\n   下载：5,678 | Stars: 42 | ❌ 未安装\n```\n\n## 示例\n\n**用户**: \"有什么 skill 可以帮我监控加密货币价格？\"\n\n**搜索**: `clawhub search \"crypto price monitor\"`\n\n**推荐输出**:\n```\n🔍 \"加密货币价格监控\" 结果：\n\n1. crypto-tracker\n   描述：加密货币价格追踪和提醒\n   下载：2,345 | Stars: 28 | ❌ 未安装\n   → 推荐安装\n\n安装命令: clawhub install crypto-tracker\n安装后验证: ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/crypto-tracker/SKILL.md\n```\n\n## v1.0.1 更新\n\n- ✅ 安装后验证步骤\n- ✅ 搜索结果显示下载量/stars\n- ✅ 检查是否已安装\n- ✅ 中文输出优化\n\n---\n\n*帮助用户发现需要的 Skills 🔍*\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776840413889}}
{"type":"message","id":"4bf52988","parentId":"d80d558a","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:46:58.795Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求学习 skill-finder-cn 技能并保存到记忆中，我已经读取了 SKILL.md 内容，现在需要用 edit 工具将新技能信息追加到 MEMORY.md 的末尾。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_7eb0f91413dd437c9a9f3026","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"MEMORY.md","edits":[{"newText":"- **记忆晋升规则：** 7 天内重复 3 次 → 升级为 HOT；30 天未用 → 降级 WARM；90 天未用 → 归档\n\n### Skill 查找器：skill-finder-cn\n\n**用途：** 帮助用户在 ClawHub 上发现和安装 Skills\n- **目录路径：** `/Users/zhu/.openclaw/workspace/skills/skill-finder-cn`\n- **触发词：** \"找 skill\"、\"find skill\"、\"搜索 skill\"、\"有什么 skill 可以...\"\n- **核心命令（需要 clawhub CLI）：**\n  - `clawhub search \"<需求关键词>\"` — 搜索相关 Skills\n  - `clawhub inspect <skill-name>` — 查看详细信息和统计数据\n  - `curl \"https://clawhub.ai/api/v1/skills/<skill-name>\" | jq '.skill.stats'` — API 查询 stats\n  - `clawhub install <skill-name>` — 安装 Skill\n  - `clawhub list` / `ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/` — 检查已安装的 Skills\n- **验证安装：**\n  ```bash\n  ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md\n  # 文件存在 = 安装成功\n  # 文件不存在 = 安装失败\n  ```\n- **输出格式：** 显示 Skill 名称、中文描述、下载量、Stars 数、是否已安装\n- **工作流程：**\n  1. 理解用户需求 → 2. 提取关键词 → 3. 搜索 ClawHub → 4. 列出结果（含数据）→ 5. 推荐最合适的 → 6. 安装后验证","oldText":"- **记忆晋升规则：** 7 天内重复 3 次 → 升级为 HOT；30 天未用 → 降级 WARM；90 天未用 → 归档"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":34029,"output":553,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34582,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776840413889,"responseId":"chatcmpl-b9b18a3c-f8d1-9c4c-adb2-6d3b5a4721cc"}}
