{"type":"message","id":"eff5f064","parentId":"7d51e658","timestamp":"2026-04-22T06:47:03.964Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"记忆更新完成后，需要向用户总结这个技能的核心信息，确认学习完成。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"学习完成！🔍 已保存到记忆 📝\n\n## 🎯 Skill Finder（中文）总结\n\n**这是什么：** ClawHub Skills 查找器，帮你在海量技能中找到需要的工具。\n\n**什么时候用：**\n- \"有什么 skill 可以帮我监控价格？\"\n- \"找一个能做 X 的 skill\"\n- \"我需要一个能...的技能\"\n- \"找 skill\" / \"find skill\"\n\n**核心命令（需要 clawhub CLI）：**\n\n1. 🔍 **搜索：** `clawhub search \"<关键词>\"`\n2. 📊 **查看详情：** `clawhub inspect <skill-name>` 或 API 查询 stats\n3. ⚡ **安装：** `clawhub install <skill-name>`\n4. ✅ **验证安装：** `ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/<skill-name>/SKILL.md`\n5. 📋 **查看已装：** `clawhub list` 或 `ls ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/`\n\n**输出格式：**\n```\n🔍 \"时间管理\" 搜索结果：\n\n1. time-management-2\n   描述：有效管理时间，避免过度工作\n   下载：1,234 | Stars: 15 | ✅ 已安装\n\n2. productivity\n   描述：生产力系统，包含目标/任务/习惯\n   下载：5,678 | Stars: 42 | ❌ 未安装\n```\n\n**工作流程：**\n理解需求 → 提取关键词 → 搜索 ClawHub → 列出结果（含下载量/stars）→ 推荐最佳 → 安装后验证 ✅\n\n以后如果你说\"找个能 xxx 的 skill\"，我会自动搜索推荐并帮你安装 🦐"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-flash","usage":{"input":34568,"output":415,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":34983,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776840418802,"responseId":"chatcmpl-083baa19-3783-96f4-98f9-475ce668eae4"}}
